-- CIT up 11 pct as says to sell housing holdings
-- 
-- Tue Jul 1, 2008 8:27am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/07/01/us-markets-stocks-beforethebell-cit-idUSN0147785220080701

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Shares of CIT Group Inc ( CIT.N ) rose more than 11 percent to $7.60 on Tuesday after the company said it agreed to sell its home lending business and other housing portfolio holdings. 

 CIT, a commercial lender, said it expected net cash proceeds of $1.8 billion from the sale.  (Reporting by  Walker Simon ; Editing by  James Dalgleish )